const functions = (props) => {
    return {
        one: props.one,
        two: props.two,
        three: props.three,
        four: props.four,
        five: props.five,
        six: props.six,
        seven: props.seven,
        eight: props.eight,
        nine: props.nine,
        zero: props.zero,

        ac: props.ac,
        eval: props.eval,
        plus: props.plus,
        multiply: props.multiply,
        del: props.del,
        minus: props.minus,
        point: props.point,
        procent: props.procent,
        plusMinus: props.plusMinus
    }
}

export default functions
